# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# zkScatter Testnet Deployment Configuration (Sepolia)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# TESTNET only. For LOCAL development use: ./scripts/dev.sh --mock
#
#   cp .env.testnet.example contracts/.env   # then fill in real values
#
# Naming: network-specific addresses use a SEPOLIA_ / MAINNET_ prefix;
# cross-network roles (deployer key, owners) stay generic.
#
# ── Two phases ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Deploy contracts (forge auto-loads contracts/.env; no key on the CLI):
#      cd contracts && forge script script/DeploySepolia.s.sol:DeploySepolia \
#        --rpc-url sepolia --broadcast --verify
#      (--rpc-url sepolia → foundry.toml [rpc_endpoints] → SEPOLIA_RPC_URL)
# 2. Run background services:
#      docker compose up -d shared-orderbook zk-relayer
#
# NOTE: DeploySepolia.s.sol (NOT DeployLocal) is the testnet script.
# DeployLocal is anvil-only — it deploys/mints mock tokens and wraps
# 1100 ETH, which reverts on a real chain.

# ── RPC (Alchemy/Infura endpoint; read via foundry.toml alias) ──
SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://eth-sepolia.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY
MAINNET_RPC_URL=https://eth-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY
ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=YOUR_ETHERSCAN_KEY

# ── Deployer key (env-signing, non-interactive) ──────────
# DeploySepolia reads this directly, so the key never appears on the
# command line / shell history / process args. gitignored (.env). NEVER
# commit. DEDICATED key funded with testnet ETH only — not your main wallet.
# Alternative (interactive password, not for AI runs): omit and pass
#   --account <keystore> --sender 0x...
DEPLOYER_KEY=0x...

# ── DeploySepolia required env (all REVERT if unset/zero) ─
# Real zk-X509 IdentityRegistry addresses — no mocks. Produced by the
# zk-X509 repo's Deploy.s.sol (MAX_WALLETS_PER_CERT=10) BEFORE this deploy.
SEPOLIA_IDENTITY_REGISTRY=0x...          # User-CA   — gates deposits / claims
SEPOLIA_RELAYER_IDENTITY_REGISTRY=0x...  # Relayer-CA — gates RelayerRegistry.register()
# Proxy admin + treasury owners. Multisig recommended; may equal the
# deployer for a quick team testnet.
UPGRADE_OWNER=0x...
TREASURY_ADDRESS=0x...
# Canonical WETH9 (structural PrivateSettlement init param). Verified Sepolia:
SEPOLIA_WETH_ADDRESS=0x7b79995e5f793A07Bc00c21412e50Ecae098E7f9

# ── Tokens whitelisted AT deploy (comma-separated, optional) ──
# Live ERC20s only (no mock deploy). Verified Sepolia USDC / USDT / TON:
SEPOLIA_WHITELIST_TOKENS=0x1c7D4B196Cb0C7B01d743Fbc6116a902379C7238,0x42d3b260c761cd5da022db56fe2f89c4a909b04a,0xa30fe40285b8f5c0457dbc3b7c8a280373c40044
# Optional: external sanctions oracle OR-combined into SanctionsList.
# SANCTIONS_EXTERNAL_ORACLE=0x...

# ── Mainnet token set (verified, for a future MAINNET deploy) ──
# MAINNET_WETH_ADDRESS=0xC02aaA39b223FE8D0A0e5C4F27eAD9083C756Cc2
# MAINNET_WHITELIST_TOKENS=0xA0b86991c6218b36c1d19D4a2e9Eb0cE3606eB48,0xdAC17F958D2ee523a2206206994597C13D831ec7,0x2be5e8c109e2197D077D13A82dAead6a9b3433C5

# ── Contract addresses (fill AFTER phase-1, from deploy summary / deployments/<chainId>.json) ──
COMMITMENT_POOL_ADDRESS=0x...
PRIVATE_SETTLEMENT_ADDRESS=0x...
FEE_VAULT_ADDRESS=0x...

# ── Relayer A ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Dedicated relayer key, minimal gas funds. Registration is NOT done by the
# deploy script — the operator registers via the operators /register site
# (KYC -> zk-X509 proof -> admin approval -> register, posting a bond).
RELAYER_A_KEY=0x...
RELAYER_A_PUBLIC_URL=https://relayer-a.yourdomain.com

# ── Relayer B (optional, multi-relayer mode) ─────────────
RELAYER_B_KEY=0x...
RELAYER_B_PUBLIC_URL=https://relayer-b.yourdomain.com

# ── Frontend ─────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_URL=https://eth-sepolia.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY
# Token list is now read on-chain via getWhitelistedTokens() (#927/#928);
# NEXT_PUBLIC_TOKENS is only a metadata/label fallback.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_TOKENS=0x7b79...:WETH:18,0x1c7D...:USDC:6,0x42d3...:USDT:6,0xa30f...:TON:18

# ── Post-deploy ───────────────────────────────────────────
# - Extra tokens beyond SEPOLIA_WHITELIST_TOKENS: owner setTokenWhitelist on
#   BOTH CommitmentPool and PrivateSettlement.
# - zk-X509: register CAs (addCA) so register()/proofs work.
